examples.en: Doctors battled to save his life.
examples.ru: Врачи боролись, чтобы спасти его жизнь.

examples.en: The battle of good versus evil
32 teams will battle it out.
examples.ru: За победу сразятся тридцать две команды.

examples.en: Her son was killed in battle.
Design a strategy for battle.
He was killed in a fierce battle.
examples.ru: Он был убит в жестокой битве.

examples.en: The battle turned into a rout.
She had battled against cancer.
He showed great heroism in battle.
examples.ru: Он проявил большой героизм в боях.

examples.en: He fought a battle for recognition.
They were vanquished in battle.
The soldiers formed into battle order.
They armed the men for battle.
The battle raged on (=continued).
examples.ru: Битва продолжалась с той же яростью.

examples.en: That two-day conflict has become one of the most famous battles in history.
examples.ru: Этот двухдневный конфликт стал одним из самых знаменитых сражений в истории.

examples.en: The troops were deployed for battle.
Few women have led troops in battle.
examples.ru: Мало кто из женщин вёл войска в бой.

examples.en: They were arrayed in line of battle.
He survived the great test of battle.
He deserted in the midst of the battle.
examples.ru: Он дезертировал в самый разгар битвы.

examples.en: The battle began with a cavalry charge.
They reenacted the battle of Princeton.
The town was shelled during the battle.
examples.ru: Во время боя город подвергся обстрелу.

examples.en: The battle took place in neutral waters.

examples.ru: В этой битве он был смертельно ранен.

examples.en: The battle continued late into the night.
The enemy are being cut up in the battle.
examples.ru: В настоящем сражении противник несёт большие потери.

examples.en: He asked whether I had been at the battle.
examples.ru: Он поинтересовался, участвовал ли я в сражении.

examples.en: They became pawns in the political battle.
examples.ru: Они стали пешками в политической борьбе.

examples.en: Two policemen were killed in a gun battle.
examples.ru: В перестрелке были убиты два полицейских.
